        <h3>Ranking Methodology & Core Criteria</h3>
        <p>This comprehensive list was meticulously compiled using extensive market data sourced in early 2026. Our proprietary rankings are primarily determined by a weighted combination of essential fundamental factors, including but not limited to overall market capitalization, trailing and forward dividend yield, and price-to-earnings ratios where applicable. Furthermore, qualitative aspects such as historical price stability, management track record, and daily trading liquidity are heavily factored into the final score to ensure that the funds listed represent viable, high-quality options suitable for mainstream retail investors. Please note that all financial data is inherently subject to ongoing market fluctuations and should be verified prior to executing any trades.</p>
